# Slopweaver work-console (generated per-user by `bootstrap_work_console` —
# `/session-start`'s first-run path). These files contain personal context
# pulled from the user's connected MCP servers and must never be committed
# to a public repo. Maintainers dogfooding slopweaver against this checkout
# are protected by these entries.
.claude/personal/
.claude/SLOPWEAVER-MEMORY.md
.claude/CLAUDE.md
.claude/commands/session-start.md
.claude/commands/fan-out-audit.md
.claude/commands/lock-in.md
.claude/commands/reconcile.md
.claude/commands/style-rule.md
.claude/commands/style-edit.md
.claude/commands/correct.md
.claude/commands/calibration-report.md
.claude/commands/recompile-profile.md
.claude/commands/decided.md
.claude/commands/focus.md
